Package module.pgpcrypto.ui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CryptoDialogFactory
    Factory for dialog boxes.
    KeyGenerationDialog
    Dialog to request user input for key generation.
    KeyRingInfoListElementPanel
    Panel that presents a nice visualization of key ring info objects.
    KeyRingInfoRenderer
    Renderer for key ring info objects.
    KeyRingSelectionDialog
    Dialog to let the user select one or more key rings from a list.
    PasswordDialog
    Shows a password input dialog with a simple password strength/quality meter.
    PublicKeyManagementDialog
    Dialog to manage public keys.
    SecretKeyManagementDialog
    Dialog to manage secret keys.
    StatusDialog
    A simple (passive) status dialog.
    TextInputDialog
    A simple dialog for text input.
    UserInterfaceElementFactory
    A factory for creating user interfaces, currently only file open and save dialog.
